---
title: Sesame Zucchini Lo Mein with Edamame plus Scallions, Wonton Strips & Spicy Mayo
description: This saucy noodle stir-fry hits the table in under 30 minutes! You'll sauté zucchini, edamame, and carrots, then toss with springy lo mein noodles and savory, gingery stir-fry sauce. All that’s left to do is top each plate with a drizzle of spicy mayo, crispy wonton strips, and sesame seeds, and dig right in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67d7e36b6526e41d967ae668-52695d75.jpeg
